    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Adrefunsus">Atrifusu</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Pasquale">Pascali</name></persName> riceve da <persName
                            ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius
                        sancte Lucane ecclesie umilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula
                        livellario nomine usque in viginti et nove annos (…) una casa cum fundamento
                        et curte totum insimul foras <rs key="#Walls">muros</rs> istius <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitatis</rs>, pertenentes <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/272" key="#Churches">Sancte
                        Marie</orgName>, prope <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Cities #Clusae/gates #Walls"><rs key="#Clusae/gates">porta</rs>
                            que dicitur Cervasi</placeName>, qui est de subpotestatem ipsius
                            <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68"><rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro</orgName>; et ipsa
                        casa cum fundamento et curte <rs key="#Confinia">tenentes uno capo</rs> cum
                        uno lato in ter[ra …] suprascripte <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/272" key="#Confinia #Churches">Sancti
                            Cervasi</orgName>, alio capo tenet in terra et fundamento de casa […, et
                        alio] lato tenet in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>; suprascripta casa cum
                        fundamento et curte (…). Suprascripta casa cum fundamento (…) usque in
                        viginti et nove annos proximi venturi mihi eas dedisti in integrum, in tali
                        ordine ut da admodum usque in suprascripti viginti et nove annos
                        suprascripta casa cum fundamento et curte in mea qui supr Atrifuso
                        presbitero et <persName><name ref="Flaipertus">Flaiperti</name></persName>
                        filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Lopo">Lopi</name></persName>, dedisti
                        potestatem eas tenendi, regendi, gubernandi et in ibi unum ex nobis abitandi
                        (…). Censo: Nisi tantum exinde per singulos annos, in mense augusto, a parte
                        suprascripte ecclesie Sancte Marie a custodem et rectorem eius dare debeamus
                        argentum denarios quatuor boni expendivilis tantum; et a mandato vestro, vel
                        de ipso custodem et rectorem suprascripte ecclesie Sancte Marie venire
                        debamus hic Luca legem et iustitiam faciendum (…). Pena: spondeo ego qui
                        supra Atrifuso presbitero conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos viginti
                        et omnes movilias nostras, que in edeficio case sunt, in nostra vel de illo
                        homines cui nos eas dederimus, dedisti potestatem exinde tollendum et
                        faciendum exinde quot voluerimus (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Sundribaldus">Suntripaldo</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ghisulfus/de Vicopelago"
                                >Ghisolfo</name> de <placeName ref="#places/3112">vico
                                Pelago</placeName></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfo</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Teudaldus">Teudaldus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>MDL, 5/2, n. 967, p. 597; ChLA, 86, n. 10, pp. 40-41</p>
            </div>
